Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Air Mattress and Beds Market

The air mattress and beds market is expected to witness market growth at a rate of 9.00% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research report on air mattress and beds market provides analysis and insights regarding the various factors expected to be prevalent throughout the forecast period while providing their impacts on the marketâ€™s growth. The increasing popularity of these products owning to various benefits they offer such as high durability and odor-free nature is escalating the growth of air mattress and beds market.

Air mattress refers to an inflatable mattress which is made from materials such as rubber material, plastic or vinyl. They are highly preferred for camping trips or occasional bedding at home for guests as they can be rolled up or folded to neatly stow away in their deflated form. These mattresses could be inflated by mouth, hand or with an electric pump and some even come with self-inflating systems. Air beds refer to dial mattresses or adjustable air mattresses which use air instead of coil system or foam core as a means of support. These offer the sleepers to adjust and customize their ideal comfort level from plush to firm through adjusting the amount of air in the chambers.

The increase in demand for these products as they are especially beneficial for people who are suffering from back pain and other bone joint-related health problems and the rise in the popularity of these mattresses and beds due to their features including ability to inflate in full size within minutes, high durability and odor-free nature act as the major factors driving the air mattress and beds market. The rise in inclination towards these products acts as a solution to sharing bed disputes and the partition of the bed between one side firmer or softer than the other in accordance to consumer preference influence the air mattress and beds market. The large availability of these products in various sizes which makes them convenient for indoor and outdoor usage and the increasing trend of remote feature allowing customers to individualize their sleep experience influence the air mattress and beds market. Additionally, reduction of indoor spaces in urban areas, use as substitute for regular beds, rapid urbanization and rise in disposable income positively affect the air mattress and beds market. Furthermore, product innovations and new launches extend profitable opportunities to the air mattress and beds market players in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

On the other hand, the lengthy time to assemble the mattresses and issues with short warranty of these products are factors expected to obstruct the air mattress and beds market growth. The concerns regarding the noise and replacement of the products are projected to challenge the air mattress and beds market in the forecast period of 2021-2028.

